(### Travel Tips for Himachal Pradesh \(April 2026\):) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 527.8899999999999864 Td
(1.  **Weather & Packing:**) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 511.8899999999999864 Td
(    *   April in Dharamshala is generally pleasant. Days are mild \(18-25°C\), but evenings can be) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 495.8899999999999864 Td
(cool \(10-15°C\).) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 479.8899999999999864 Td
(    *   Pack layers: light woolens, jackets/hoodies for evenings, comfortable cotton clothes for) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 463.8899999999999864 Td
(the day.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 447.8899999999999864 Td
(    *   Carry comfortable walking shoes/sneakers, especially if you plan to trek or do a lot of) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 431.8899999999999864 Td
(walking.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 415.8899999999999864 Td
(    *   Sunscreen, sunglasses, and a hat are essential.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 399.8899999999999864 Td
(2.  **Transportation:**) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 383.8899999999999864 Td
(    *   **Booking:** Book your train/flight tickets and initial taxi transfers well in advance,) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 367.8899999999999864 Td
(especially for April which is a popular travel month.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 351.8899999999999864 Td
(    *   **Local Taxis:** For 4 adults, hiring a private taxi for the entire trip is most convenient but) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0. g
48. 335.8899999999999864 Td
(will consume a significant portion of your budget. Alternatively, use shared taxis or local) Tj
